    public class MaterialWindow
extends gwt.material.design.client.base.MaterialWidget
implements com.google.gwt.event.logical.shared.HasCloseHandlers<Boolean>, com.google.gwt.event.logical.shared.HasOpenHandlers<Boolean>
    Window is another kind of Modal but it has a header toolbar for maximizing and close the window. Also you can attached a tab component on its content.

    XML Namespace Declaration

     xmlns:ma='urn:import:gwt.material.design.addins.client'

    UiBinder Usage:

     <ma:window.MaterialWindow ui:field="window" />

    UiBinder Usage:

     // Opening a window
  window.openWindow();

  // Closing a window
  window.closeWindow();
    Author:
    kevzlou7979
    See Also:
    Material Window
